# Control Fields

ğ’ (_ControlField_) is a _named control_ for which a unique name is assigned by the system.
When the text field of ğ’ is edited, the new value is sent to the synthesiser.

ğ’ is both a part of the definition of the program and,
while the program is running,
an interactive controller for the synthesiser.
